1. Poštujte *pravila* o zdravlju i higijeni. (Respect the rules regarding health and hygiene.)
2. *Pravilima* je zabranjeno parkiranje u ovom delu grada. (Parking is prohibited in this part of the city by the rules.)
3. Da bi ste postigli uspeh u poslu, morate se pridržavati *pravila* igre. (To succeed in business, you must abide by the rules of the game.)
4. Ova organizacija ima stroga *pravila* o radnom vremenu i radnim obavezama. (This organization has strict rules regarding working hours and duties.)
5. *Pravilima* konkursa je određeno da su prijave otvorene do 15. marta. (The rules of the competition specify that applications are open until March 15th.)
6. Ako ne poštujete *pravila*, bićete kažnjeni. (If you don't follow the rules, you will be punished.)
7. Učenici moraju da se pridržavaju *pravila* ponašanja u školi. (Students must abide by the rules of conduct in school.)
8. Ovaj sport ima mnogo *pravila* koja se moraju naučiti pre igranja. (This sport has many rules that must be learned before playing.)
9. *Pravilima* je propisano da se na ovom događaju ne smeju koristiti mobilni telefoni. (The rules prescribe that mobile phones should not be used at this event.)
10. Ako želite da budete uspešni u životu, morate se pridržavati određenih *pravila*. (If you want to be successful in life, you must follow certain rules.)